Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是尾形游紀的女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個天才尾形的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這次是她的初次演出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像舞台的換場一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2025年 被稱為GGP的反抗組織一夜間統領了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級大國和反抗組織
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇視心與巨大的戰力差距
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPP憑藉著新戰力的投入顛覆了戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得了歷史性的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 這些英雄們的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能被世人所見證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是埋沒在了「歷史性勝利」這一詞彙中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就從前台褪去了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後對新世界秩序的構想降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀰漫著敵意的武裝力量 報復的連鎖反應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及它的擴大…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到希望 灰色的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,革命 新的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算是那個已經在變化著的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也無緣觸及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依著母親的叮囑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上將上天賦予我的生命拚命的跳著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光 這感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在這個舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才感受到自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帷幕在不覺中落下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:57.70,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:57.70,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:10.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:24.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:41.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:41.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:49.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:49.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
